HEADWORD: Toxodon
<hw>Tox"o*don</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>to`xon</grk> a bow + <?/, <?/, a tooth.]</ety> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld>
<def>A gigantic extinct herbivorous mammal from South America, having
teeth bent like a bow. It is the type of the order
<ord>Toxodonta</ord>.</def>⟦br⟧
